flowchart TB
    subgraph RationMateApp[RationMate Application]
        P1(Login & Profile Mgmt)
        P2(Entitlements & Schemes)
        P3(Shop Status)
        P4(Complaints)
        P5(Admin Mgmt)
    end

    User -->|Login, View data, Submit complaint| P1
    User -->|Check ration info| P2
    User -->|Check shop| P3
    User -->|Submit complaint| P4

    Admin -->|Manage alerts, schemes, holidays| P5
    Admin -->|Resolve complaints| P4

    P1 --> Database
    P2 --> Database
    P3 --> Database
    P4 --> Database
    P5 --> Database
    Database --> P2
    Database --> P3
    Database --> P4
    Database --> P5
